{"tid":1675571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理Post] 告急！過嚟問下啲區議員候選人喇喂","createTime":"2019-10-26T03:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T04:32:08.000Z","uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"128ffc1a62e5a16314a04bf4c4cc816c46750910","tid":1675571,"uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:48:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有六日咋</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六日！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六日！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六日！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=e5d287ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6</a><br />\n<br />\n我都知係冇乜人會理我，問啲區議員又關我鬼事咩<del>，我又識條鐵咩</del>。<br />\n只不過作為香港人，我唔忍心依家關我事嘅嘢，慢慢變到唔關我事。<br />\n我能力有限，無能力要求個個人都應我，但我只係想用和理非名義，去問問我哋依家要選既區議員候選人，究竟佢哋點解值得代表香港人。<br />\n<br />\n如果結果係出email佢哋唔覆機，其實唔緊要，歷史會話俾我哋知，佢地連佢地自己嘅選民都可以迴避，唔配代表我。<br />\n～完～"},{"pid":"cf565368e7b4b969b4795571c817879dc8efd20c","tid":1675571,"uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"2019年區議會選舉將至，為了更了解候選人的理念，「有種責任」決定向各候選人以電郵方式發問。所有問題都會以匿名形式記錄，歡迎大家留下問題，我們會代為發問。<br />\n<br />\n所有收集所得的資料會在選舉後一個月內刪除，不會轉讓給第三方人士。<br />\n<br />\n關於我們：敝平台「有種責任」並非主流傳媒，僅由數名關心香港的「九十後」青年於今年6月開立，並於在不同的網上平台包括：Facebook、YouTube、Instagram及Telegram，向市民發佈新聞資訊。<br />\n<br />\n如有任何疑問，歡迎以電郵方式聯絡。謝謝！<br />\n電郵地址：HKOneResp@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n歡迎Share出去，讓更多人提供問題。<br />\n截止日期：2019年10月31日<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=e5d287ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6</a>"},{"pid":"9733f8e4a9b2c6c33f431bc3f81860822df3fe78","tid":1675571,"uid":19984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"我宣布，十點鐘鳩嗌，正式回歸！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ctu4WC0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtu4WC0.jpg&h=0f6b4f14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRihxbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRihxbm.jpg&h=cb7e0abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQCx5yp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQCx5yp.jpg&h=0ff71da6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}